{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Conduct review of treatment of teachers in schools & colleges & mitigations",
        "additional_details": "We believe cameras in class rooms, independent audits of administrative practices and school leadership processes could help provide teachers with a better work environment. The Government should conduct a review and present its findings to Parliament. I have chosen to share my story openly through a short film called Swallow exposing harsh realities rarely seen on screen.",
        "background": "We believe there needs to be a review of the treatment of teachers in schools, and consideration of whether new policies and frameworks could better protect them from abuse.",
